<!--pages/micro_mall/buy/modules/tipsPopup/tipsPopup.wxml-->
<window class="window" ext-class="window-ext">
	<view class="main {{isIphoneX?'ipX':''}}" style="{{boxStyle}}">
		<view class="box"><text class="_bold">本单可用红包</text>
			<block>为当前订单中可用的红包额。</block>
		</view>
		<view>遇到红包不在结算时抵扣时，可参考如下：</view>
		<view class="box"><text class="_bold">1.确认可用时间：</text>
			<block>是否未到使用时间或者已过期</block>
		</view>
		<view class="box"><text class="_bold">2.确认可用金额：</text>
			<block>订单总价扣减优惠后（如优惠券）是否满足红包的使用</block>
		</view>
    <view class="flex_global flex_c">
      <button bindtap="close" style="background:{{brand_info.style.bg_color}};" hover-class="none" class="btn">知道了</button>
    </view>
	</view>
</window>